description:
Magneto's first own ongoing series. Magneto returns to his role as protector of Mutant-kind after he left the X-Men team in issue 16 of Uncanny X-Men Vol 3. Magneto gatheres a group of like-minded in his war against people whom commit mutant-related crimes. The series lasted for 21 issues and ended due to the events of Secret Wars.

Collected Editions

  • Magneto: Infamous (#1-6)
  • Magneto: Reversals (#7-12)
  • Uncanny Avengers: AXIS Prelude (#9-10)
  • Magneto: Shadow Games (#13-17)
  • Magneto: Last Days (#18-21)
  • Secret Wars: Last Days of the Marvel Universe (#18-21)
name: Magneto

description:
Preceded by Volume 3. The white knight of the moon rises again in his newest ongoing series! Moon Knight was recently in Los Angeles but he makes his return to New York City. This series delves deeper into Moon Knight's different personalities and origin. It lasted for 17 issues and was continued a half year later in an All-New, All-Different series (Volume 5).

Written by:

  • Warren Ellis (#1-6)
  • Brian Wood (#7-12)
  • Cullen Bunn (#13-17)

Drawn by:

  • Declan Shalvey (#1-6) (covers only: #7-17)
  • Greg Smallwood (#7-12)
  • Ron Ackins (#13-14, 17)
  • Steven Sanders (#14)
  • German Peralta (#15-16)

Collected Editions

  • Moon Knight: From the Dead (#1-6)
  • Moon Knight: Dead Will Rise (#7-12)
  • Moon Knight: In the Night (#13-17)

Translated into Spanish.
name: Moon Knight
